title: Surviving Mars Digital Deluxe Edition
description:
Description:
Have you long dreamed of a new simulator of town planning? So Surviving Mars is for you. The colonization of Mars is increasingly rising in many books, films, and now the game is also presented to your attention. Since the developers of such a cult simulator as Tropico have taken on this project, then the game promises to be decent. Colonizing Mars - the idea seems to be not easy, but no one said it would be easy. The vast experience of the creators and their latest developments will definitely allow this creation to gain the look of a full-fledged urban planning simulator with its own features and tricks
